Package: eden
Version: 0.6.0
Section: editors
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: EdenX <hello@edenx.dev>
Homepage: https://edenx.dev
Description: EdenX terminal text editor
 A fast, minimal terminal text editor with support for encrypted files.
 .
 Features include:
  - AES-256-GCM encrypted file format (.ednx)
  - Syntax highlighting for 16 languages
  - Mouse support (click, scroll, tab bar)
  - Multi-buffer tabbed editing
  - Incremental search and replace with regex
  - File navigator overlay
  - Multiple color themes
  - System clipboard integration
